Concept:

Survival, base-building, loot collecting....?

Mix of LDOE, and Rust.

During the daytime, player can loot, gather resources, and build up the base.

At night, it's dangerous to go out. Wolves and Badgers roam and can attack the player, break down the base
and destroy player made deployables.


